{
  "stem": "5188.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think he was the only one who really felt that things were not going to get any better.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they were in the general area, but not in Surth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- I had aunts and uncles in the neighboring town, Rodenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had aunts and uncles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had-- one family was in Rheinbach, one in Schweiz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All of these towns were, I would say, within one or two hours of driving.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to get together for parties, birthday parties.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to celebrate my parents' birthday all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have any kids' parties in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But for my parents' birthday and for the other people's birthdays, we would go there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, there were bar mitzvahs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were weddings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the family always got together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the family got together, and we would visit, the talk was almost always about the politics, what's going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were some Jewish people who were joining the Hashara.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, the Hashara was the Jewish organization to go and work on a kibbutz in Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And here, something did develop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know exactly when it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe it was 1934 or '35-- maybe it were-- I don't know exactly-- when non-Jews could no longer work for Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, that meant that Ketchen, my very dear housekeeper, and Fritz-- Fritz worked in the store, and--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fritz was the man who worked in the store with my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Non-Jewish man, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they lived in our house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were sleep-in help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were really part of the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And unfortunately, they had to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And actually, I went back to visit them in 1970.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now that was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a very happy reunion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It really was.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
